      "markdown": "## 4、 划线部分是“时间”，特殊疑问词whattime或when \n\n如:It's seven twenty .---What time is it?\n\nIusually get up at six.---When do you usuallyget up?\n\n## 5、 划线部分是“年龄”，特殊疑问词howold \n\n如:Iam twelve.---Howoldare you?\n\nMyfather is thirty-three .---How old is your father father?\n\n## 6、 划线部分是“职业”，特殊疑问词用what Y \n\n如:Mike is a worker.---WhatisMike \n\n7、划线部分是“颜色”特殊疑问词用what colour \n\n如：Myhat isblueWhat colouris your hat?\n\n### 8. 划线部分是“数量”，特殊疑问词howmany或howmuch \n\n如:I can see five kites .---How many kites can you see?\n\nThere is some milk in the glass.---How much milk is there in the glass?\n\n### 9. 划线部分是“多少钱”，特殊疑问词howmuch \n\n如:This pen is nine yuan .---How much is this pn?",
